---
title: Southeast Asian-Style Chicken & Tofu Noodle Soup with Baby Broccoli & Coriander
description: On a cold winter night, a soup is always the best go-to dinner option. Strings of yummy noodles will go down smoothly with golden spiced tofu and veggies in a creamy coconut broth. This bowl of soup will have you feeling warm in no time.
